    <release version="4.5" date="2024-02-20">
      <description translatable="no">
        <p>Planify 4.5 is here, design improvements and new features available.</p>
        <p>What‚Äôs New</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Nextcloud integration is available.</li>
          <li>Snap support thanks to @soumyaDghosh</li>
          <li>Option to migrate tasks from Planner</li>
          <li>Redesigned date and time selection widget</li>
          <li>It is now possible to move tasks by dragging them to the task list</li>
          <li>Option to show completed subtasks always</li>
          <li>Added option to hide sections.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>Bug Fixed and Translations</p>
        <ul>
          <li>German translation add thanks to @bestlinuxgamers</li>
          <li>Russian translation update thanks to @hachikoharuno</li>
          <li>Turkish translation update thanks to @sabriunal</li>
          <li>Bugs fixed #1123, #1122, #1121, #1106, #1126, #1113</li>
        </ul>
      </description>
    </release>

    <release version="4.4" date="2024-01-10">
      <description translatable="no">
        <p>Planify 4.4 is here, design improvements and new features available.</p>
        <p>What‚Äôs New</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Improved drag-and-drop sorting: Added a new animation and a new way of sorting making it cleaner and easier.</li>
          <li>Support for sub-projects: Create a sub-project just by dragging and dropping or by using the magic button and dropping into the parent project.</li>
          <li>Magic Button: Just drag and drop to add tasks wherever you want and in the order you want.</li>
          <li>Board View: Have an overview of your tasks without losing sight of the details.</li>
          <li>Using Adw.OverlaySplitView to have a collapsible sidebar.</li>
          <li>Sections are now created from a Dialog and support color and a description.</li>
          <li>Parent and child tasks: It is now easier to create subtasks, just drag the child task to the parent task and drop it.</li>
          <li>New preference to configure whether to add the task at the beginning or end of the list.</li>
          <li>Quick Add now allows you to select the target section.</li>
          <li>Improved integration with Todoist, now allows you to create tasks with strange character content.</li>
          <li>The description of a project is now editable instead of using a Dialog.</li>
          <li>The design of the reminder creation has been improved.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>Bug Fixed and Translations</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Portugu√©s translations thanks to @godinhoana54.</li>
          <li>Russian translation update thanks to @hachikoharuno.</li>
          <li>Turkish translation update thanks to @sabriunal.</li>
          <li>Bugs fixed #1089, #1081, #1099, #1087, #1009, #1008, #1007.</li>
        </ul>
      </description>
    </release>

